{"tid":1453560,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"暴動可能打得甩","createTime":"2019-08-12T04:36:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T04:47:10.000Z","uid":9148,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f3e8deff5778aa0d5ef4e6babae6b75563206dc6","tid":1453560,"uid":9148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:36:39.000Z","msg":"POPO扮示威者，上庭可以推個波去POPO度，疑點利益歸於被下告下？ <br />\n有冇得諗？"},{"pid":"6cc2bf74fd4b3a9239d3c34a86789223c87210ac","tid":1453560,"uid":4462,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:37:58.000Z","msg":"香港行內地法好耐啦，要自己證明自己無罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f30dd8cc8527c439aa96d2ac9742a1b1b65fe6f","tid":1453560,"uid":9148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cc2bf74fd4b3a9239d3c34a86789223c87210ac","tid":1453560,"uid":4462,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:37:58.000Z","msg":"香港行內地法好耐啦，要自己證明自己無罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:43:27.000Z","msg":"雖則好灰，但都要堅持"},{"pid":"f913b361791cc7e3fbbd4c36d7aa7288dabbce4a","tid":1453560,"uid":103102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:43:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港需要人道救援</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當下，香港極需要不受滋擾的中立醫療團隊。我們需要無國界醫生、聯合國維和部隊，以及其他人道救援組織。只有他們可以為香港提供正常醫療保障，免於中共香港警察滋擾。以下這個聯署，是要求美國派遣醫療船以提供中立的醫療服務。美國醫療船扺達後，其他國際醫療組織就更易來港協助，以減低香港人在今次戰爭的傷亡。<br />\n<br />\n這是十分實際的要求，也是極為急切和重要。為免香港發生大規模人道災難，請各位簽署並廣傳！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-send-medical-army-hong-kong-hong-kong-under-humanitarian-disaster\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-send-medical-army-hong-kong-hong-kong-under-humanitarian-disaster&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpC8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=959367b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-send-medical-army-hong-kong-hong-kong-under-humanitarian-disaster</a>"},{"pid":"43dbd56bca64a695beb1b3e5e8725b5a50e842db","tid":1453560,"uid":63406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:46:39.000Z","msg":"佢地扮示威者<br />\n根本成件事就冇咩程序公義可言<br />\n<br />\n屌你老尾黑警"},{"pid":"f6b416832f7fa286f46548a1a008555f5085149f","tid":1453560,"uid":73262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7f30dd8cc8527c439aa96d2ac9742a1b1b65fe6f","tid":1453560,"uid":9148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cc2bf74fd4b3a9239d3c34a86789223c87210ac","tid":1453560,"uid":4462,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:37:58.000Z","msg":"香港行內地法好耐啦，要自己證明自己無罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:43:27.000Z","msg":"雖則好灰，但都要堅持"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:47:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}